Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That you'll become the next president.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never be president...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said you won't let me\Nhave my way with Suletta anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you given up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take over your precious Quiet Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your father will be pleased too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'd better promise me that\Nyou won't involve Suletta any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But please allow Suletta and Aerial\Nto take part in one more duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One more?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This will be the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, you can do\Nwith her as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, will that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,really give up Aerial so meekly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:27.00,OS - TNR,SIGN,0,0,15,,{\an8\fs24\fad(1000,1)}Episode 17
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good... morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you waiting all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I, uh... just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not suspended from school anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday marked one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:02:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I said something weird the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,About...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I asked you to get rid of Aerial,\Nwhat would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Aerial is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,family to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine,\Nit's almost your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you like to celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My wish list includes\Ncelebrating a friend's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to give it a try...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you turn 17, Ms. Miorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.50,OS - TNR,SIGN,0,0,0,,Benerit Group Front
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:51.17,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,Because you're negotiating\Nwith the kidnappers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you now think you're\Nhis successor, Shaddiq Zenelli?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In the upcoming presidential race,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to run on behalf of Grassley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I'd like to form\Na partnership with Peil Technologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting ahead of yourself.\NWhat's in it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll support Gundams as a new\Ncore business for the Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundams?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll transfer GUND-ARM, Inc. to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you developed Pharact in secret\Nviolation of the Cathedra Agreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this can't be a bad deal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we get the Aerial, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the sales plan to you.\NYou can enjoy the actual benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does Sarius feel about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That man would never\Naccept such an about-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Council won't stay silent either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bear the brunt of the criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,\Nwe're Cathedra's biggest investor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't participation in the Gundam business
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing you most desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarius won't be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mio--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Elan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come in here!\NThis is Ms. Miorine's--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you give me Aerial?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. You can be my savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You like me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you are now, Mr. Elan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Elan this, Elan that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The man you're thinking of isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over Aerial to me, immediate--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Elan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none other than the runaway prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:06:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I never could figure you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go showing off\Njust because there's a girl here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ruin this place,\Nno apology will get you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you quit school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lauda went behind Dad's back\Nand held off my withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was able to re-enroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A-About your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am really deeply sorry about his loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. I have a purpose now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to rebuild the Jeturk company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing left\Nthat ties me to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard what's happened to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,At least... I've heard it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I spoke to Lauda and we decided\NI'd take over as president.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The company is on the brink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to us to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,any more of the things precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Precious... things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as my re-enrollment is complete,\NI'll return to the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, I wanted to visit\Nthe school one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologize\Nto everyone in Jeturk House, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you tell this\Nto someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Move forward, gain two."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I... finally understand how frightening\Nit is to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I was scared that\NI kept running away from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I can move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me how.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I d-didn't do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But still... I'm a little glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I love those words, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that was the part of you\NI fell for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But before you said\Nyou didn't like me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was... How can I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Then I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,have someone precious to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice you have someone\Nyou can say that about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is, uh... not what it--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.04,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,I've decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what I want for my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A duel between you and Guel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the gift of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.20,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself, Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,am finished with dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to run\Nfor president of the Benerit Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you and the Jeturk company\Nto support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second! Where is this going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your company...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to rebuild it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become your fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, the Group is sure\Nto fully support the Jeturk company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're telling me to win the duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The things precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Guel Jeturk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Reclaim your bride...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,from Suletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Both parties, deposit\Nyour souls on Libra's scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The duelists\Nare Suletta Mercury and Guel Jeturk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The location will be\Nthe 13th tactical testing sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The one-on-one code will apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:38.90,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sir... you haven't\Nquit school after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to extend\Nyour record of losing like a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jeturk emblem is the lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So call me a lion, not a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what is your stake in this duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help stop\Nthe harassment of Earth House?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the Open Campus,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone in Earth House\Nhas been treated like a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If the students from Jeturk House\Nwould take our side...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Guel Jeturk,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what is your stake in this duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with Aerial, Mr. Guel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alea jacta est.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The duel is approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,About Suletta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you really did like her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her how I feel. Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more important things right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of her, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said about her mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta doesn't question\Nanything her mother says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She was only sent to this school\Nto fight duels in Aerial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want that girl to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs a world where she can be\Nfree from Gundams or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no worlds like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one thing to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me some scissors and clippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really gonna duel like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was confiscated during our suspension.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have no money for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! If only Nika were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\NMs. Miorine's gone missing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this.\NMy work schedule was moved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No... it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine said it would\Nbe a victory charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay focused. I'm rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel sorry for her?\NShe was rather fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe you're saying that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,\NI'll give you the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please look forward to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Guel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was damaged anyway. You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Guel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I did my best to optimize it,\Nbut what about that AI?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care. Leave it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride alone won't defeat Suletta Mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We couldn't find the right timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And? How far have you gotten with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lauda...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As your older brother,\NI've never done a thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still count on my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I told you when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Connection established\Nwith Carrier Gate No. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Guel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Guel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}MS container is authorized to launch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We will now begin the duel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As always, victory will go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the first one to break the blade\Nantenna of their opponent's mobile suit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The observer shall be me,\NSecelia Dote of Burion House.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Guel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to start.\NAren't you gonna watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see any more fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just back home\Nand already so hot-blooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Guel hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, his objective must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The restoration of the Jeturk company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this your doing, Miorine?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No objects in vicinity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlocking MS containers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}KP001, Guel Jeturk...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}LP041, Suletta Mercury...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Darilbalde...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Moving out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:35.66,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taking off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial is back in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Enhanced Person Number Five has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They were worried about you...\Nyour Earthian friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It occurred to me during the Rumble Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Gundams and Grassley\Nmust be in cahoots," I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I snooped around,\NI was right on the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not welcome at Peil now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're all fugitives,\Nlet's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not get in a Gundam and die already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to live a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Being killed by you\Nor dying in a Gundam aren't in my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dying... in a Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Both parties, face off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is never decided\Nby mobile suit performance, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor by the skill of the pilot, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.56,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The result itself is the only truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,15,,{\i1}The result itself is the only truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.56,OS - TNR,SIGN,0,0,0,,13th Tactical Testing Sector
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fix release.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,First I have to close the range!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with Guel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't he shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it, Brother? Trouble of some kind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.\NI'll snap out of it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Delling's daughter... was pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Bel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Mr. Guel feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Guel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.12,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,Mr. Guel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He blocked it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Guel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guel! Are you okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Guel, you're as strong\Nas I thought. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... Override?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promised.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For Miorine's birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promised I'd win!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said I'd stay at her side forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it's my turn to ask her that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll buy rings together\Nand have a wedding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we'll both wear the very best dresses!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please choose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.68,Default - On top,,0,0,0,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in you... Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta... lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do, Aerial?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's Ms. Miorine's birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I promised I'd win...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! I... Aerial...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She stopped moving all of a sudden, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was me who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you from the beginning, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a good shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, you can't fulfill\Nyour obligations if you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Guel! Please duel with me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time... I won't lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that back too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye,
